00:36:41,165 --> 00:36:44,498
Hey, Susan.
You gotta try this. It's a vegan cupcake.

504
00:36:44,602 --> 00:36:45,728
Thank you, but I'm fine.

505
00:36:45,836 --> 00:36:49,829
Oh, come on,
you gotta try it. It's delicious. There.

506
00:37:02,386 --> 00:37:04,479
You know what happened, don't you?

507
00:37:04,589 --> 00:37:08,423
They put me on the green team
with Greg and Paul.

508
00:37:08,526 --> 00:37:10,585
Two of the oldest guys in this division.

509
00:37:10,695 --> 00:37:14,529
I feel like
I've been put in with the dinosaurs.

